Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:14.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I… I went too hard…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:23.40,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have… run that much along with those two…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:26.02,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I played at the beach all morning…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.02,0:00:28.44,Kaho,,0,0,0,,and then we did so much practice…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:32.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,my HP is pretty much zero now…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.64,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The beach is terrifying…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.22,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The temptation to play too much is too strong…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:46.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Rurino-san, I know it isn’t much, but I wanted to help in whatever way I could, so I tried looking it up.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:53.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Even if a physical injury is healed, the mental trauma left behind can prevent someone from returning to performing.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This occasionally happens to figure skaters as well.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:01.05,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.05,0:01:04.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That can still be healed… right?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:07.46,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:12.47,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,However, the way that happens varies from person to person, so…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:23.67,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,One thing I will say, Rurino-san, is that your plan to bring back her drive to perform…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.18,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,is something that has already been shown to be effective.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.31,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, really!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.31,0:01:32.16,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:33.95,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:36.68,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…But?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.25,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.99,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,While it is true that a fun performance can help her overcome her trauma,\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,the reverse is also possible…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:53.22,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That is to say, if your performance were to end in failure…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:58.62,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It is very probable that it would only exacerbate the problem.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:10.01,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s also very likely Kozue-senpai falling from the stage a few months ago also made Megumi-senpai’s trauma resurface.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:13.53,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,And although nothing serious came of the incident,\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:18.86,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that you mean a lot to Megumi-senpai…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:20.60,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,so…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:24.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If I… were to fail…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:32.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don’t worry{\i0}, Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,There’s no way I could fail.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.00,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I… see…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:40.96,Rurino,,0,0,0,,This is for Megu-chan, after all!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:46.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m sure you can see just how pretty she is, and how good her fashion sense is,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,and how nice her voice is, and how amazing her smile is, right?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:53.70,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Um…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:59.96,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but she has the smarts and incredible moves.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:04.95,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And her conversations are always so interesting that she always draws a crowd with them!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:09.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And she even used to be a TV personality, too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,She’s shown up on a bunch of TV shows!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.72,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, I see…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:16.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:21.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,She can do anything, and she’s always been amazing!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:25.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That’s why everything will turn out okay!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.75,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that she’ll be able to overcome this, too!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:33.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I… I believe in her.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…You share a strong bond, hm?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.51,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Of course, we’ve been together since grade school!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:47.78,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Alright!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:52.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,The training camp isn’t over yet, so why don’t we get to bed!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:56.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Or maybe you guys wanna do something else? Like a classic pillow fight?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:01.80,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Hehe… I’m pretty good at those, you know.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:05.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you think you can handle it, huh!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.34,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sure.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.31,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Back when I was following in my sister’s footsteps,\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.16,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I used to go to figure skating training camps fairly often.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:18.19,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It was a regular occurrence with the other kids my age when we would stay in a big room together.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Alright, in that case!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Kaho-chan, let’s go!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,H-Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.47,Kaho,,0,0,0,,B-But my body’s still so sore, and–\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.03,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Here goes!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeet!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.51,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Wha–!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.30,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Kaho-san…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Yikes, did we kill her!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.85,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Fine!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:58.43,Kaho,,0,0,0,,If that’s how you wanna do this, then I’ll use up all my energy for tomorrow, right here, right now!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.70,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna make you blossom!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.09,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.07,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Aah!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:05.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&}Ahahaha!  \N{\fs40}[Kaho & Sayaka & Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.15,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…haa… haa…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And then we can have fun together again!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:29.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let’s have fun together again, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll definitely catch up to you!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:45.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Seriously, what am I doing?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Why am I still like this…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
